Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…牙齿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植根于先祖血肉内的植物之苗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸展开茂盛繁盛的枝叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而结出丰硕累累的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能卖我点吃的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这田地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏天出奇的冷天气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结出的粮食已经非常少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱指望啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山那头的村子看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年只有那里丰收了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别出鬼点子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的米没有问题才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾年还能丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是先祖的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的丰收…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的丰收…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有谁要被先祖带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年会是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先祖会优先选择身体虚弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…这田真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是想问问有没有多余的粮食能卖给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可没有多余的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是每年都能收获足够的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要储粮时还是得储粮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今年的丰收算是奇迹…咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直有好好地祭祀祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九泉下的祖先也一直保护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须有个人被带走…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是先祖该做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是…没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没试过怎么知道没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能跟我说说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子的田地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大灾年的时候丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是很早以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当年秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有人的嘴里长出「瑞齿」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种牙齿会在秋天结束时掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人也会…随之死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那人的生命也认为是从先祖那里获得丰收的祭品…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种说法一直这样流传着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大家还是感谢先祖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有这个奇迹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许没办法在这片贫瘠的土地上一直生存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选中的人有什么共同点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说都是从身体虚弱的人开始选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体是土葬吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落的牙齿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑞齿」都被祭师师父供奉在祭堂里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责村里一切祭奠活动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会继承祭师的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被教导各种祭祀事务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑞齿」脱落不久  就只有祭师师父能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  必须由祭师师父来举行祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么要继承祭师的位置呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和祭师师父一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常…能看到常人看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你说的那个祭师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭师师父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在田里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农耕的书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有日记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是虫师银古
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找寻「破落的果实」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙乐  你现在应该在田里干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.90,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(注：这里音译的人名「サネ」即为「実」，日文意义中的「果实」)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干完再回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年是丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好准备可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  还在担心你妈的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把这个拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说很久以前也有虫师来过我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只是白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里根本没有那种果实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你也相信丰收是先祖显灵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先祖显灵吗？当然有这原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家因为强烈的信仰才能在这块土地上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来我们也在一直研究使土地肥沃的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此有时也会有这样的大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年的粮食产量也在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  「瑞齿」你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人成年后还会有可能继续长牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和种地没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能问问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该知道「破落的果实」的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我从长辈那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个虫师封印在「光脉」里的东西…据说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也能感觉到「光脉」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有能看见「虫」的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虫」就是这种发光的微小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虫」的根源与「光酒」相近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓「光脉」就是「光酒」流淌的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是「生命」的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运用得当的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生或复活什么的都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是虫师最大的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也会有例外出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种果实就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在土里的话就能使周围获得一年的丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代价一个生命体将会被带走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是我们虫师之中流传的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你找到那果实的话你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭它？还是利用它？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的话你会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道牺牲一人便能拯救更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而获得这种果实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会利用它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这种果实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼见很多人饿死就是罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知有一人会死还是种下果实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等同于杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被拯救的人再多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的人也只是作为祭品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人还是会做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去一个人的性命就能拯救两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一年这么短时间的话确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用过一次后就会想用第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那果实是会成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随使用次数增加它的影响力也会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会把一切的平衡破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是说不要用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样闲置而不用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也没在这里生活过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事态恶化前还是离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地里还埋葬着先祖的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖祖辈辈的辛勤的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渗透在每一片土地里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们而言是唯一的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道种下了异形的物种的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不算是对这片土地的玷污吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是万一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的出现那种果实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会…慎重考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的果实只会使一个人无法存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而收获的稻穗则会垂下重重的头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注定会从耕者的掌心滑出  洒落在这土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后  人类的悲欢离合  它们永远感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们谈完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你会帮我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过需要得到全村人的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我得先把「诅咒的丰收」有关的一切内情告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把大家集合起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  到底为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想劝大伙烧掉田地吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在再次有人长「瑞齿」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把果实消灭的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于承认了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧了田地的话谁都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把大家都饿死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要搬离这里一年就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一时分散到其他土地上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一年的话应该能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天烧剩的灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能使土地肥沃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会有几人会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家因为不知道内情才会忍耐至今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都以为真的是先祖显灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不允许谁对大伙胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭师师父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你师父得了什么病吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是最近他总是身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时就要喝药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个罐子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你为何会喝这种毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想就这样死掉来逃避责任吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫师先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要烧田时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出你的目的不是那种果实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我成为那种果实的最后的牺牲者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说把「破落的果实」带到村子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上上任的祭师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  每逢灾害的时候就使用这种果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免不必要的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种果实的存在只有代代的祭师才能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从我做了祭师后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决意不再使用这种果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到二十年前那场天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还得用那果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我只是想村里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有注意到妻子瞒着我身体不适的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长了「瑞齿」的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要吃田里的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你也死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的命能让你存活的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死也不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我咀嚼着这样的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体只是贪婪的吸收着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子脱落的「瑞齿」变成的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算扔掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又想到总有一天又会有天灾降临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次使用时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到谁牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于天灾又降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来我体内结出的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算交给沙乐处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种果实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果埋入你所说的「光脉流」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会融入里面而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说不清楚那到底是种什么果实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该比任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想在这里活下去  看到村子的将来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不懈努力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地会慢慢肥沃起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天人们不靠这种果实也定能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道这将是多少代之后的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我估计是看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如你所愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你再回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭师师父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了饭后人也精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说不会有事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沙乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么今年的祝词和往年不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  现在还没有人长「瑞齿」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还没有听说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的丰收不是「诅咒的丰收」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道是我们努力的成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭奠很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会照您的嘱咐做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭师师父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说光酒是生命的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是并不代表直接饮用就能让人复活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使之成为现实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种果实应该行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是我猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吃掉那果实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物复活的事应该也能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和植物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕光脉会成为你身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越生物的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你能接受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你们最大的禁忌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做这种事难道会被允许吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不说的话不会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成功与否我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道这样后你能否幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  只是赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是加重你的伤  而确定这种果实的存在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样玷污我的手也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考虑考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不必考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…果然还是想看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地的将来会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是凭自己的努力会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在村里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片土地上的人们为这次丰收雀跃不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一则奇妙的传说流传开来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久的「诅咒的丰收」没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年结出的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使一个男人起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来那个男人不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游遍各国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片土地就会再现生机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他是回去传授新的耕作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}栖砚之白
